# Action OS spine (locked focus)

Full spec: `docs/ACTION_OS_SPINE.md`

## Only build this loop

```
Context (calendar · notification · chat · link)
  → @ Action Contract Registry
  → Proactive prep surface (MAIN + AUX)
  → Archive fold + telemetry
  → Learning rollup → MAIN ranking
```

## Active (in order)

1. **@ registry** — App Intents–style `featureId`, slots, MAIN resolver, `sourceRef`
2. **Proactive sharpen** — prep/calendar SSOT only; sharper domain + MAIN
3. **Context maintain** — four ingest axes only (no 5th)
4. **Archive → ranking** — rollup feeds MAIN resolver on prep surface

## Frozen — do not implement

- Life Replay / archive UI
- Server-side archive sync
- Screen ambient / vision context
- New ingest path (5th context axis)
- Domain LLM action candidate expansion before `@` registry is fixed
- Silent Ghost / Figma bridge (other repo)

## Reject in review

- Parallel event stores or suggestion surfaces outside prep/calendar
- New `sourceRef` families beyond calendar / notification / chat / link
- LLM action domains not registered in `@` contract registry
- Archive UI or server sync work
- Importing Ghost truth-log / projection / site patterns

## Substrate (never remove)

EventCandidate SSOT, lifecycle + fold gate, confirm/slot collect, telemetry 4 kinds, NL ingress as fallback to same contracts.
